name: Silnas-Dem
content:
Silnas-Dem was a male Weequay who worked as a heavy armor merchant during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. During the war, he operated a stall in the Alien Enclave Market of the city Voss-Ka on the planet Voss. Silnas-Dem wore brown clothing while at his stall and spoke a language other that basic to customers. He had brown skin, black hair and blue eyes.
Silnas-Dem first appeared in Star Wars: The Old Republic, an MMORPG released by BioWare in 2011. In the game he serves as a Republic and Imperial heavy armor vendor on the planet Voss. His location is also marked on a map in Prima Games' Star Wars: The Old Republic Explorer's Guide.
